
Softwares Required:
	Visual C++
	Microsoft Windows
	OpenGL Library

Instructions:
	
	After installing visual C++ do the following:
	
		(1)	Copy and paste all the header files ( .h ) and
			library files ( .lib ) to the include directory and 
			library directory of Visual C++ installation directory.

		(2)	Copy and paste all the dll files ( .dll ) to C:/Windows/System32

Creating a new project:
	
	File --> New --> Project --> Win32 Console Application --> Finish

	In the solution explorer right click on source files and choose
	add from existing file and choose Move_Light / movelight.cpp

Run
	F5


